                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="fdf781cf59bc492695c50bad22495d80">
                    <h2 data-uuid="404a695f42ee4c54ac44f7aea4efc184">Effects of the Atom Bomb on Hiroshima</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="a4bac5add4c04445ae843304dfdbe40a">The atomic blast over Hiroshima killed many of its residents and left the city in ruins. Rubble from homes and factories stretched for miles.</p>
                </div>
